Table 1. Crystal data for the title compound

| Molecule formula | C30H54Mo12N6O46PGd |
|------------------|-------------------|
| fw               | 2574.29           |
| Crystal size, mm | 0.24×0.21×0.20     |
| Crystal system   | Monoclinic        |
| Space group      | Pn                |
| Z                | 2                 |
| a, Å             | 12.950            |
| b, Å             | 13.236            |
| c, Å             | 19.070            |
| β, °             | 100.78            |
| V, Å³            | 3211.0            |
| d calc, Mg/m³    | 2.663             |
| μ/mm⁻¹           | 3.407             |
| Total no. of reflections | 13,109    |
| Independent reflections | 13,101 (R int=0.0587) |
| R1, wR2 (all data) | 0.0317, 0.0625[^a] |
| R1, wR2 [I>2σ(I)] | 0.0275, 0.0619[^a] |
| Largest difference peak and hole, eÅ⁻³ | 0.994 and −1.925 |

[^a]: w⁻¹=[σ²(Fo)²+(0.0303P)²] (P=(Fo²+2Fc²)/3).
